'''盗蜜'''是指[[昆虫|昆虫]]、[[鸟类|鸟类]]或其他[[动物|动物]]在[[植物|植物]]的[[花瓣|花冠筒]]上直接打洞取食[[花蜜|花蜜]]，但不给花[[授粉|授粉]]的现象<ref name=biods.2015102>{{cite journal|last1=Du|first1=Jiaxiao|last2=Meng|first2=Lu|last3=Sun|first3=Haiqin|last4=Bao|first4=Ying|title=Effects of nectar robbing on pollinator behavior and pollination success in facultative selfing Incarvillea sinensis var. sinensis|journal=Biodiversity Science|date=2015|volume=23|issue=5|pages=658–664|doi=10.17520/biods.2015102|doi-access=free}}</ref>。

被盗蜜植物主要是具有[[长花管|长花管]]或花上有[[蜜腺距|蜜腺距]]的[[产蜜植物|产蜜植物]]<ref name=biods.2015102 />。存在盗蜜现象的植物大约有59科214种<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Irwin|first1=Rebecca|last2=Maloof|first2=Joan|title=Variation in nectar robbing over time, space, and species|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_oecologia_2002-12_133_4/page/525|journal=Oecologia|date=2002-12-01|volume=133|issue=4|pages=525–533|doi=10.1007/s00442-002-1060-z|subscription=yes}}</ref>。常见的盗蜜者是[[蜂类|蜂类]]，尤以[[熊蜂|熊蜂]]和[[木蜂|木蜂]]为多，在美洲一些鸟类也是常见的盗蜜者<ref name=biods.2015102 />。

盗蜜会损坏植物生殖器官[[柱头|柱头]]和[[花药|花药]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Irwin|first1=Rebecca E.|last2=Bronstein|first2=Judith L.|last3=Manson|first3=Jessamyn S.|last4=Richardson|first4=Leif|title=Nectar Robbing: Ecological and Evolutionary Perspectives|journal=Annual Review of Ecology, Evolution, and Systematics|date=2010-12|volume=41|issue=1|pages=271–292|doi=10.1146/annurev.ecolsys.110308.120330|subscription=yes}}</ref>, 还能通过影响传粉者的行为来影响植物的[[适合度|适合度]]<ref name=biods.2015102 />。此外，通过影响传粉者行为，盗蜜者会增加[[花粉|花粉]]的散布距离、促进[[异交|异交]]<ref name=biods.2015102 />。

